<br>
My mission here today is simple, I seek assistance in regulating this flaw and in my opinion, one of the best and most logical ways in doing so would be to commission a Blacksmith who would be able to make some form of superior Breast Armor to the one I currently adorn.<br>
<br>
Should you be interested, be aware that I am a Human Paladin and am seeking some form of armor in the range of 40 (AC) or higher with accompanying stats including Strength and if possible agility and dexterity. <br>
<br>
As for financial compensation, money is not really an issue as I have, and can quickly acquire more, (if need be). I am not willing to state a price here and now, however, I am willing to accept bids via in game tells. The individual that manages to contact me with the most interesting offer will of course, win this contract. I can be reached in game via the name deathwatch or via email at aodablaze@hotmail.com<br>
